这里是常用参数设置区，包括描述词、画幅及图片存储设置。值得注意的是，由于整个工作流程主要依靠IPAdapter和ReVision相结合，来控制画面的输出，所以大多数情况下，描述词并不需要精细调整，只需要非常精简的描述就可以了。


Here is the common parameter setting area, including prompt, frame size and image output storage settings. It is worth noting that since the entire workflow mainly relies on the combination of IPAdapter and ReVision to control the output of the image, in most cases, the prompt do not need to be finely adjusted, only a very concise prompt is required.

此处是额外的LoRA及Control Net堆栈，默认是Bypass状态，因为大多数情况下，进行头脑风暴时不需要这些，除非您想进行更精准的设计，那么可以打开，并添加必要的节点和模型来进行精确控制。

Here are the additional LoRA and Control Net stackers. The default is Bypass state, because in most cases, these are not needed for brainstorming. Unless you want to make a more precise design, you can open it and add the necessary nodes and models. for precise control.

蓝色区域为这个工作流程的核心工作区，多数情况下不用做调整。当然，您可以在此指定特定的主模型和细化模型，以及采样参数等。如果您对IPAdapter和ReVision熟悉的话，也可以根据自己的需求来调整它们的各项权重。


The blue area is the core of this workflow, and in most cases no adjustments are needed. Of course, you can specify specific main and refiner models here, as well as sampling parameters, etc. If you are familiar with IPAdapter and ReVision, you can also adjust their weights according to your own needs.

这个工作流程的核心是将IPAdapter和ReVision整合到一起，然后通过16张用户预先准备的参考图，让AI帮我们进行各种设计的头脑风暴。


The core of this workflow is to integrate IPAdapter and ReVision, and then let AI help us brainstorm various designs through 16 reference pictures prepared by users in advance.
